g\">What is prompt engineering?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#why-prompt-engineering-matters\">Why prompt engineering matters?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#basics-of-prompt-engineering\">Basics of prompt engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#the-prompt-engineering-lifecycle\">The prompt engineering lifecycle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#inference-parameters\">Inference Parameters</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#zero-shot\">Zero-Shot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#few-shot\">Few-Shot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#chain-of-thought\">Chain of thought</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#self-consistency\">Self-Consistency</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#general-tips-for-designing-prompts\">General Tips for Designing Prompts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#common-misconceptions-about-prompts\">Common Misconceptions About Prompts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#prompt-generator-tools\">Prompt Generator Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#reasoning-model-ie-openai-o1deepseek-r1\">Reasoning Model (i.e. OpenAI o1/DeepSeek R1)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br/>\n<strong>Key Takeaways:</strong><br>\nPrompt engineering is an \ud835\uddf6\ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf2\ud835\uddff\ud835\uddee\ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf6\ud835\ude03\ud835\uddf2 \ud835\uddfd\ud835\uddff\ud835\uddfc\ud835\uddf0\ud835\uddf2\ud835\ude00\ud835\ude00 involving continuous \ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf2\ud835\ude00\ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf6\ud835\uddfb\ud835\uddf4, \ud835\uddfa\ud835\uddfc\ud835\uddf1\ud835\uddf6\ud835\uddf3\ud835\uddf6\ud835\uddf0\ud835\uddee\ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf6\ud835\uddfc\ud835\uddfb, \ud835\uddee\ud835\uddfb\ud835\uddf1 \ud835\uddfc\ud835\uddfd\ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf6\ud835\uddfa\ud835\uddf6\ud835\ude07\ud835\uddee\ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf6\ud835\uddfc\ud835\uddfb. As models continue to evolve, prompts must adapt accordingly to maintain effectiveness.</p>\n<p><br/></p>\n<h1>What is prompt engineering?</h1>\n<p>Prompt engineering is about \"communicating\" with LLM in a way that maximizes the model's understanding and performance on a given task. At its core, prompt engineering involves designing, refining, and optimizing the text inputs (prompts) given to models to elicit accurate, relevant, and useful responses.</p>", "image": "https://dannyzheng.me/assets/images/social/2025/02/21/prompt-engineering.png", "date_modified": "2025-05-07T06:43:08+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Danny Zheng"}], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://dannyzheng.me/2025/05/06/the-future-of-engineering--ai/", "url": "https://dannyzheng.me/2025/05/06/the-future-of-engineering--ai/", "title": "The Future of Engineering & AI", "content_html": "<h1>\ud83d\ude80 The Future of Engineering &amp; AI \u2014 Insights from CEOs</h1>\n<h2>Michael Truell - CEO of Cursor</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"We're not going straight to a world where AI does everything...</p>\n</blockquote>", "image": "https://dannyzheng.me/assets/images/social/2025/05/06/the-future-of-engineering--ai.png", "date_modified": "2025-05-07T06:43:08+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Danny Zheng"}], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://dannyzheng.me/2024/10/15/cursor-ai-done-right-lessons-from-building-multiple-mvps/", "url": "https://dannyzheng.me/2024/10/15/cursor-ai-done-right-lessons-from-building-multiple-mvps/", "title": "Cursor AI Done Right: Lessons from Building Multiple MVPs", "content_html": "Cursor AI Done Right: Lessons from Building Multiple MVPs", "image": "https://dannyzheng.me/assets/images/social/2024/10/15/cursor-ai-done-right-lessons-from-building-multiple-mvps.png", "date_modified": "2025-05-07T06:43:08+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Danny Zheng"}], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://dannyzheng.me/2024/10/15/whats-model-context-protocol-mcp/", "url": "https://dannyzheng.me/2024/10/15/whats-model-context-protocol-mcp/", "title": "What's Model Context Protocol (MCP)", "content_html": "Model Context Protocol (MCP) is an open protocol that standardizes how applications provide context to LLMs.", "image": "https://dannyzheng.me/assets/images/social/2024/10/15/whats-model-context-protocol-mcp.png", "date_modified": "2025